properties.areaDesc: Natrona County Lower Elevations; Green Mountains and Rattlesnake Range
properties.headline: Special Weather Statement issued January 2 at 12:23PM MST by NWS Riverton WY
properties.description:
This is a special weather statement from the National Weather
Service Office in Riverton.

* WHAT...Southwest wind 35 to 40 mph with gusts up to 60 mph.
Higher gusts up to 70 mph are possible over Outer Drive.

* WHERE...Portions of Natrona County, including the Casper area.

* WHEN...From Saturday morning to early Saturday evening.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Travel will be difficult, especially for
high profile vehicles. Strong cross winds will enhance the
blowover risk for lightweight and high profile vehicles,
including camping trailers.
